# PostCSS Rem To Rpx [![Build Status][ci-img]][ci]

[PostCSS] plugin transform rem to rpx for miniprogram.

[PostCSS]: https://github.com/postcss/postcss
[ci-img]:  https://travis-ci.org/ZhangCheck/postcss-rem-to-rpx.svg
[ci]:      https://travis-ci.org/ZhangCheck/postcss-rem-to-rpx

```css
.foo {
    margin: 0.3rem 5rem;
}
```

```css
.foo {
    margin: 0.3rpx 5rpx;
}
```

## Usage

```js
postcss([ require('postcss-rem-to-rpx') ])
```

See [PostCSS] docs for examples for your environment.
